Cost Optimization â†’ auto shutdown idle resources.

âœ… Shows real DevOps value in interviews.

ğŸ”¹ 5. Security & Best Practices

Use virtual environments (no global pip installs).

Never hardcode secrets â†’ use env vars / Vault.

Use black / flake8 â†’ code formatting.

Add error handling & retries for API calls.

Version control â†’ store scripts in GitHub.

